title: Bunch of changes.
message:
Bunch of changes.

Updated OpenCV for Android SDK to 2.4.5.
Created my own CameraBridge and JavaCameraView since OpenCV ones were limited
and not customizable.
Custom rules to Ant instead of separate scripts to rsync JNI files and run
ndk-build.
Added rule to not display BPM lower than 40.

title: Performance improvements and simple signal validation.
message:
Performance improvements and simple signal validation.

Face detection is done only every 10 frames.
Detrend is not done if raw signal is too noisy (stdDev > 10).
Bpm is not calculated if number of peaks is too low (or high) and stdDev is too
large (> 0.5).
Created a deploy file to copy files to Android JNI folder.
